Description: American Standard Stratocaster Guitar Good Condition. Tweed Case Included. Condition is Used. Shipped with UPS Ground. With the Fender Deluxe Strat, classic style and modern electronics crystallize into a first rate solid body electric guitar. Noise free, highly articulate Vintage noiseless single coil pickups deliver the classic Stratocaster chime you know and love. A discrete mini switch activates the bridge pickup in positions four and five, unlocking a world of new sound. If your a fast lead player, you'll love the Deluxe Strats comfortable modern C shaped neck and flat 12 inch radius fingerboard. Complete with nickel/chrome hardware, a three ply B/W/B pick guard and aged white pickup covers, control knob and switch tip, the Fender Deluxe solid body electric guitar is a flexible tone machine!. Note-the finish on this guitar is not high gloss as might be expected brand new. Held up to the light there are slight blemishes which makes me suspect that it was repainted before I purchased it, resulting in more of a matte than glossy finish. In any case, this can only be detected under close inspection under bright light. It still looks and plays amazing!
